name: Zodiac Coffee & Co Karangasem
address: Jl. Achmad Yani No.32, Subagan, Kec. Karangasem, Kabupaten Karangasem, Bali 80811, Indonesia
review 1: Charming cafe with a cozy atmosphere and friendly staff. Delicious coffee and pastries, the rice bowl was nice, perfect for a relaxing break or catching up with friends. My new favorite spot in town!
review 2: The nicest and most eye catching coffee shop in the town. We are here for a short break after lempuyang temple trip. Nice coffee i had an ice americano which is not bad at all. And a piece of extra dark choco cake. Place is nice to chill.
review 3: This place is a gem in the middle of karangasem. It is not just the only cafe that serves absolutely delicious cappuccino and lattes but it also has a great selection of desserts. It is extremely affordable and the wifi was great so you can sit down and work here. I would highly recommend
review 4: Make this your next stop for a good morning start. Good, friendly service with very interesting selection of hot and ice coffee. Treats are yummy. Vibe is chill. Rings all the right chimes for a Bali pit stop.
review 5: We had a great experience! The staff was super nice and it was fun seeing them being excited about music. They seem to be a good team which is essential for a good service. We had fries, a sandwich and a latte. The fries were outstanding! The cappuccino was amazing too, we would definitely come again!
